[[Brejik]] wore a personal '''belt''' during combat which, when used in conjunction with [[Brejik's Arm Band|his arm band]], produced a mild, though effective, barrier against [[Melee weapon/Legends|melee attacks]].<ref name="KOTOR">[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]</ref>

In [[3956 BBY]], his belt was recovered by [[Revan/Legends|Revan]] and [[Bastila Shan]] after they [[Death/Legends|slew]] Brejik and the rest of the [[Black Vulkars/Legends|Black Vulkars]] at the [[Tarisian Season Opener]] [[Swoop racing/Legends|swoop race]].<ref name="KOTOR" />

